source.name: Better Brakes - Manufacturers Reporting
source.description: This dataset contains information reported as part the Better Brakes Law, Chapter 70.285 RCW. It contains the number of manufacturers who reported and the number of formulas they reported on as required by the Washington State Better Brakes Law.

datasets.name: Better Brakes - Formulas Reported
datasets.description: This dataset contains information reported by manufacturers of brake friction materials as part the Better Brakes Law, Chapter 70.285 RCW. It contains the number of manufacturers who reported and the number of formulas they reported on as required by the Washington State Better Brakes Law.
